org.tensorics.core.commons.options

Interface Environment<S>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of the scalar values (elements of the field on which the operations are based)
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    QuantityEnvironment<S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnvironmentImpl

    public interface Environment<S>
    Encapsulates a field (on which alll calculations are based) and a set of options, since the two are very commonly used together and have to be passed on on many occasions.
